      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUNTERVIEW JACK (3) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (30.14) in a Maiden at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Likely to improve sharply this time. MAXIMUM NANA (4) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at Nowra over 365m behind Stop And Stare (22.22) in a Maiden. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Has ability and can measure up. BARKLEY LANE (1) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 272m behind Swiper Lane (16.58). Comes through a solid form race last start. Likely to be about the money. RHYNO'S GIRL (7) will be hard to beat despite making her debut at this circuit.",
